== command position offers the executable and the directory, not the data file:
./run
./sub/
./zz_path_dir/
./zz_path_exec
== argument position still offers every file:
./data.txt
./run
./sub/
./zz_path_data
./zz_path_dir/
./zz_path_exec
== PATH command completion offers only the executable
zz_path_exec
== a blocked first PATH entry does not hide a later executable
zz_path_blocked
